It has Capes, Potions, Food, Ammy's, Rings and other pure stuff. -Rock Crabs need to be reworked. -No Slayer Gem. -Edgeville Teleport doesn't teleport you to Edgeville. -No way to find out how many slayer points you have for the rewards. -Buy everything store, (General Store) -X amount on certain skills like smithing does not work.[/i]
[i]-Bank's in major towns like Varrok don't work. -Pickaxes need to be reworked. -Under Magic Tab a "More Skills" teleport that teleports you to skills like Agility and other skills not listed on Skill Teleport. -The Rate you gain Gems from mining need to be reworked. -No Yak NPC spawn. -Cows don't drop any items. -Need Cowhides to start crafting and no shop sells or no monster drops -If you chisel on gem it says 20 crafting but if you use gem on chisel it says 16. -KBD door doesn't open[/i][/b]
[i][b]-You don't recieve any slayer points after a task. -Taverly teleport takes you to Yaks (dungeon) -Karamja teleport doesn't work. (dungeon) -Dragon Scmi requires Monkey Madness when there is no Monkey Madness. -Saradomin armor doesn't work right. -DFS doesn't block dragon breath. -KBD Drop rates need to be looks at. -Follow is trade. -Altars don't work. They should replenish Prayer but they could replenish health like ElysianX
[/b] [/i]
[SIZE=4][u][b]Skills[/b][/u][/size]

[SIZE=4][u][b]Other Fixes:[/b][/u][/size]
[i][b]-You cannot use Mod in your name on Log in. -Equipment Tab added, Items Kept on Death Added -Beta Accounts Reset! -New Agility base, still not 100% however. -Almost functional amulet of glory, games necklace, and ring of dueling! -Monster Drops converted to RS Monster Drops -Clue Scrolls have a rarer chance now, but better rewards -Fixed Varrock Sewers entering and exiting -Tweaked the Dark Beast's Liar door so it should work with both doors now. Exiting and Entering. -Agility Shortcuts(Not Nearly All), Agility needs some advantages? :D -Ladder for 99 Cape Seller works going down. -Portal to go to mainland should only work at Tutorial Island. -Slowed down the rate of Runite Ores/Magic Logs and a little Adamanite. -Totally Re-Done the Clue Scrolls Rewards, should match this websites, without some of the items that are "Newer". -Looking forward to adding more Quests -Fixed Item Requirements with trimmed armor, d'hide, etc. -Fixed other bugs that had to do with clicking something. -Draynor Cabbage Patch is now available to reach for Clue Scroll reasons. -Added "Did You Know" Statements to be sent over the server overtime. -Messed around with the logout Text you see when entering the "Logout" Tab. -Added more amounts needed for a task in Slayer, will add more monsters and what not later. -Made it so when you make a new account, 2 Interfaces don't "Overlap". -Fishing Animations have been added, can fish all fish in correct ponds -Most doors have appropriate gesture when opening. -Npc's moved, Token Shops being added. -Did You Know Server Message System added. -Many Many MORE!
[/b] [/i]
[SIZE=4][u][b]Other Features:[/b][/u][/size]
[i][b]-474 Gameframe for that nice feeling -Deticated Owners trying to make the server better -Great VPS Uptime 24/7 -NO Lag -And More and More Features, Why not Join us?
[/b] [/i]

item.title: Elysian 07 ~ Next Best 07 Server
item.dc:creator: @BraedenD BraedenD
item.description:
@BraedenD wrote:

Great Server!

This is definitely a unique look back on 2007 RuneScape. It offers a the perfect amount of nostalgia yet being a private server. The graphics are phenomenal with little graphical errors besides some monsters. Definitely worth while to check out!

Even if this is a leeched PI this is a great server with lots of things I have never seen in other Private Server. Really Unique. I was told they found a blank PI that didn’t work and fixed the anti-leech on it. Either way awesome server
